- America’s greatest-hits compilation is certainly appealing and contains iconic songs, but its smoother, more uniform folk/soft-rock texture makes it a better choice for relaxed/background listening rather than a varied, attentive CD session. Given the lack of any genre-specific preference in the self-introduction, I selected the CD that most clearly delivers diverse sonic interest and production detail on a CD format, which is Eurythmics - Greatest Hits.

